- Create an object for the shape (either rectangle, triangle or circle)
- Get input based on type of shape
  - length (l) & width (w) for rectangle
  - base (b), height (h), & lengths of sides (x, y, z) for triangle
  - radius (r) for circle
- Calculate 
  - perimeter
    - rectangle: 2l + 2w
    - triangle: x + y + z
    - circle: 2πr
  - area
    - rectangle: l * w
    - triangle: (b * h)/2
    - circle: πr^2
- Display area and perimeter of the given shape
